otnote" id="note21-"><span class="label">21. </span><p data-aid="138779693" id="note21_p1">Véase<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.html?verse=20#p20" href="/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.20?lang=spa#p20"> 2 Nefi 31:20</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.html?verse=29-30#p29" href="/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.29-30?lang=spa#p29">Mosíah 26:29–30</a>; <a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.html?verse=42-43#p42" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.42-43?lang=spa#p42">Doctrina y Convenios 58:42–43</a>; Boyd K. Packer, “<a class="cross-ref" data-old-href="../../../../general-conference/2015/04/the-plan-of-happiness.html" href="/general-conference/2015/04/the-plan-of-happiness?lang=spa">El plan de felicidad</a>”, <em>Liahona,</em> mayo de 2015. El presidente Packer dijo: “… cuando el proceso del arrepentimiento es completo, no quedan cicatrices gracias a la expiación de Jesucristo”.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note22-"><span class="label">22. </span><p data-aid="138779697" id="note22_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.html?verse=20#p20" href="/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.20?lang=spa#p20">2 Nefi 31:20</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note23-"><span class="label">23. </span><p data-aid="138779701" id="note23_p1">Véase<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/ot/josh/24.html?verse=15#p15" href="/scriptures/ot/josh/24.15?lang=spa#p15"> Josué 24:15</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note24-"><span class="label">24. </span><p data-aid="138779705" id="note24_p1">Julie B. Beck, “<a class="cross-ref" data-old-href="../../../../general-conference/2010/04/and-upon-the-handmaids-in-those-days-will-i-pour-out-my-spirit.html" href="/general-conference/2010/04/and-upon-the-handmaids-in-those-days-will-i-pour-out-my-spirit?lang=spa">… y sobre las siervas derramaré mi Espíritu en aquellos días